cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.MM, cs.RO, cs.HC 

Reasoning: 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with 3D human pose estimation from camera views. 
- cs.GR (Graphics) is also likely as the paper discusses up-scaling of volumetric body shape. 
- cs.MM (Multimedia) is another possible category as the paper deals with processing of visual data. 
- cs.RO (Robotics) is a possible category as the paper mentions potential applications in passive human behavior monitoring. 
- cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction) is another possible category as the paper deals with estimation of human body shape and pose, which could have implications for human-computer interaction.
